Leaving Los Angeles 
🔹It’s official. At the end of the month I’ll be leaving LA. It’s been an amazing almost 8 years here. I’ve had some incredible highs and some tough lows but all in all I’m thankful for it all. Grateful for all the experiences, achievements, & lessons. I will continue my acting journey in my next destination. To all my friends that I’ve made here I appreciate you for being on this journey with me. I’m really gonna miss this place but I’ll definitely be back in the future. It’s not goodbye just see you later. (And if you wanna hang one more time before I go you got the number) 😏 All prayers and best wishes welcomed for my next move. Until next time Bye LA! 😎✌🏽 
🔸Next stop: ATL 🍑
2023 it’s all about me. Making moves and going after everything that’s mine. #nextchapter #newbeginnings
